Class NewOrderImpl

java.lang.Object
  NewOrderImpl
All Implemented Interfaces:

public class NewOrderImpl
extends java.lang.Object
implements NewOrder

The NewOrderImpl class implements NewOrder Interface, it represents a new order. The NewOrderImpl class includes methods for getting and setting symbol, size, orderId and limitPrice of an order.
